<H3> <TI>   UNITA's Savimbi Absent </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0702153794 Lisbon RTP Internacional Television in 
Portuguese 1200 GMT 7 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0702153794 </F>
<F P=104>  Lisbon RTP Internacional Television </F>


