<H3> <TI>   French President Mitterrand Leaves Yamoussoukro </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AB0802095094 Paris AFP in French 2132 GMT 7 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> AB0802095094 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yamoussoukro, 7 Feb (AFP) -- French President 
Francois Mitterrand left Yamoussoukro (220 km northwest of 
Abidjan) today at 2115 GMT after attending the funeral ceremony 
of Ivorian President Felix Houphouet-Boigny and participating in 
the minisummit of countries of the franc zone. 
  The Concorde took off for Paris with former French President 
