Messmer and Jacques Chirac. Mr. Chirac arrived in Yamoussoukro 
yesterday with French Prime Minister Edouard Balladur. Mr. 
Balladur is to leave Yamoussoukro aboard a Falcon-900 plane a 
few minutes after Mr. Mitterrand. 

