<H3> <TI>   DP Urges TEC To Reconsider </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB0702184594 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1600 GMT 7 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0702184594 </F>
