<H4>   TEC Comments on Criticism </H4>
<F P=102> MB0802192594 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1600 GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0802192594 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


