<H3> <TI>   Government Asked To Stop Cameroonian Incursions </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AB1202131594 Lagos Radio Nigeria Network in English 0600 GMT 
12 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AB1202131594 </F>
<F P=104>  Lagos Radio Nigeria Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] A renewed appeal has been made to the federal 
authorities to take necessary measures to check incursions into 
Nigerian territory by Cameroonian gendarmes. A community leader 
in Akwa Ibom State, Mr. Godwin Obote, told newsmen in Lagos that 
