Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Mr. Siye Abraha, minister of defense, called on 
donor governments and organizations to assist the efforts being 
made to rehabilitate members of the defense force of the 
transitional government, who would be reduced as part of the 
reorganization of the new national defense force representing 
