Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report from correspondent in Lusaka] </F>
  [Text] This morning, the National Union for the Total 
Independence of Angola [UNITA] presented its position on the 
general principles of national reconciliation. In the 
afternoon, the government delegation went to the Mulungushi 
Conference Center to counter the superfluous contents of the 
