Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] War is the reality in the city of Malange, which 
continues to be shelled by the National Union for the Total 
Independence of Angola [UNITA]. Yesterday, two children lost 
their lives and two homes were extensively damaged as a result 
of the shelling. Francisco Coringama, our correspondent in 
Malange, reports: 
