the city and the airport with eight B-12 cannon shells. Some 
people were killed, but I hope to provide more details in 
upcoming casts. 
  Yesterday, two children were killed and another two wounded, 
as a result of UNITA's shelling. Two homes were extensively 
damaged [words indistinct] told the local radio station that an 
artillery piece was neutralized. It should be noted that the 
government forces are still in control at this stage. [end 
recording] 

