<H3> <TI>   Prefect Bans 18 Feb March by Opposition Party </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AB1702231294 Dakar Radio Senegal in French 2200 GMT 17 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> AB1702231294 </F>
<F P=104>  Dakar Radio Senegal </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Communique issued by the prefect of Dakar on 17 February] </F>
  [Text] The prefect announces that the proposed march by the 
And-Jef/African Party for Democracy and Socialism slated for 
tomorrow, 18 February, has been banned for the following reason: 
threat to public order. 
  Any violations of the provisions of the present order will 
be 
punished in accordance with the laws and regulations in force. 

</TEXT>

